verbose_text: Some of the NotchDeltaE / EGFP targeted cells on the olfactory nerve are Pdgfrb positive but Sox10 negative (black / white arrowheads, XREF_FIG E-E 2) : these may have originated from NotchDeltaE / EGFP targeted developing OECs that have already down-regulated Sox10 expression, or NotchDeltaE / EGFP targeted frontonasal mesenchyme cells that have colonised the nerve.
